{"tid":1591240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一遍地開花","createTime":"2019-09-24T05:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:03:46.000Z","uid":62025,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"12dcad0f7bec0c9f56d79b15b1c3321e7f38dda3","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"by 洗淨鉛華&bull;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遍地開花十大好處：<br />\n一、避開水炮車<br />\n二、分散警力<br />\n三、方便進場，唔洗靠港鐵<br />\n四、自己區攪冇藉口唔出黎（人數有保證）<br />\n五、方便退場，唔洗靠港鐵<br />\n六、各個港鐵站都可以成為目標<br />\n七、各個政府建築物都可以成為目標<br />\n八、將示威帶到社區，街坊掩護<br />\n九、熟悉地形<br />\n十、政府最撚驚8.5黎多劑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n必須承認出港島作用極少，失敗同被狗捉機率極高<br />\n手足願意番去七月尾八月初果陣真正be water未？"},{"pid":"a103327931fac733f0152a1ea71a43db65f2d2c2","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c60d4cfeb653d6a8b38c97bc33f047a7ccbca516","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1a940e97219b416f13a947520ec90e778042062","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f73d0b84aa8d1e5299c53c115492ce40ebe4171a","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"就算係和理非大遊行，有齊不反對通知書<br />\n有幾和平都好，啲狗都可以一開始就舉旗，己經冇得應對<br />\n只有十八區先係最撚勁，帶裝落場都安全，不服來辯"},{"pid":"a9ccd016483755d499367bdbbe667acabe5e0597","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfd8844b40670b3ea0686f35df755acdde355698","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94d68e9bf27a557c9f069370c7ea3658184de1fb","tid":1591240,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49e3